      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SKINNY MARIE (1) looks close to another win after finishing second from Box 4 last time (23.31) at this track. Top prospect. SUDDEN SURPRISE (8) was sent out long odds last time but charged out of the boxes with a strong early sectional and went on to clock 22.51 in a neck win at Gosford over 388m. Has performed well from this box with a win and four minor placings to his name from nine starts. Form should stack up. FASCINATE VERN (2) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing third behind Reborn Scarlett (23.17) in a Grade 5. Took the lead and boxed on but run over. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Can measure up. ELLA KNOWS (5) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to turn the form around.",
